title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Lunchbox and Morgan Going to Repay Her Debt (Week of 6/14)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Lunchbox and Morgan Going to Repay Her Debt (Week of 6/14)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 brings on Lunchbox to talk about how they did a bit where they went to a grocery store with him posing as her dad making her apologize for accidentally stealing paper towels.
